{"tid":743166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反DQ集會　劉小麗誓言贏回一席","createTime":"2018-07-15T07:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:23:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab74961cc29c9ed54ecdcbcdc1b7b1a7eb2e414","tid":743166,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180715/20450221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F20450221&d=A7PZhSMhbKKmWPPLr8B8doM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=501c1ea0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F20450221&h=d3817961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180715/20450221</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月15日 <br />\n<br />\n反DQ集會　劉小麗誓言贏回一席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180715/large/15la6p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180715%2Flarge%2F15la6p2.jpg&h=e2bd8aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主派昨在立法會示威區舉行反DQ一周年集會。何頴賢攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】4名前立法會議員梁國雄、劉小麗、羅冠聰和姚松炎去年7月14日被褫奪議員資格，民主派昨在立法會示威區舉行反對禠奪議員資格一周年集會，約百名市民參與。不少發言的嘉賓提到要贏回九西一席，有意在11月補選代表民主派披甲的劉小麗指不論在任何崗位，她都會為民主派贏回一席。<br />\n<br />\n昨日集會因雨勢太大由公民廣場移師到立法會示威區舉行。佔中九子之一、社福界議員邵家臻透露佔中案將在11月開審，他已有準備自己和同案被告公民黨陳淑莊或會被判即時入獄，DQ議員將由6人增至8人，呼籲市民要留意眼前危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n約百人出席　梁國雄：人數理想<br />\n<br />\n4位去年被DQ的議員壓軸發言，劉小麗指，若沒有足夠的民主派進入議會，現時留在議會的議員所承受的壓力會更大，她呼籲市民勿放棄，並在年底的補選支持民主派。劉之後補充，香港正風雨飄搖，不能只看自己的個人得失，要為大局承擔，她不論在任何崗位都會為民主派贏回一席。<br />\n<br />\n集會後，被問到參與集會人數不似預期，會否擔心民主派在補選中難以集氣，梁國雄解釋，由於前日不少人出席劉曉波逝世追思會，同時集會開始的時間過早，出席集會的人數理想。他又強調今次並非為補選動員，只是紀念活動。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180715/large/a1202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180715%2Flarge%2Fa1202a.gif&h=1898a374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今年初立會港島區補選中被DQ參選資格的周庭昨亦有出席集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180715/large/a1202b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180715%2Flarge%2Fa1202b.gif&h=9617a497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n單眼出問題難察覺遺傳影響大　七成初小生需戴眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n團體倡馬路鋪LED　提低頭族「轉燈」"},{"pid":"f619824b72aee0b7285a5952335b6ef76329ce0f","tid":743166,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母DQ4<br />\n明明就DQ6"},{"pid":"859a741a8ade091c39a647dc3fcf16181bdb10ba","tid":743166,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f619824b72aee0b7285a5952335b6ef76329ce0f","tid":743166,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母DQ4<br />\n明明就DQ6"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講係DQ11"},{"pid":"7cd52a7b823c44eb644684761d2805b678a8117c","tid":743166,"uid":41658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"對劉小麗真係冇好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d664ac684375d4a68f58ea6d5a2429a049d58b0","tid":743166,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"聽住先，佢喺立法會成日做柒嘢之前，唔知大家會唔會比多次機會佢試，拭目以待"},{"pid":"1b0404eeafd96f1e4fe11231535bfb89b5da9ad8","tid":743166,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc0bca32485d986d856879c516af80e07f5f213b","tid":743166,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201